commit.message:
DOC: Autoreformat all the docstring to match the numpydoc format. (#1324)

* DOC: rogue space is bad numpydoc formatting.

This space made numpydoc _think_ the parameter is part of the
description of `count`.

* DOC: Autoreformat all the docstring to match the numpydoc format.

This uses a prototype project of mine, so might be incomplete, and try
to be better at understanding (and reformatting, docstrings complient
with numpydoc.

I understand that you would be opposed to large scale reformatting.

This is on top of #1323 which made numpydoc choke on the docstring and
prevented correct reformatting.
